data.description: Welcome to your beautifully remodeled sanctuary nestled conveniently by The Golf Club at Fernley and free from HOA fees, this property provides both convenience and freedom, promising a lifestyle of leisure and flexibility.This spacious four-bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home with a coveted loft offers the epitome of modern living. The kitchen, adorned with  stunning new stainless steel appliances, granite/quartz countertops, and a center island, invites culinary creativity and social gatherings. This home is an entertainment Haven, with generous, multi-purpose rooms including a great room adjacent to the kitchen and a separate dining area  (Currently used as an office), this home offers ample space for gatherings and relaxation.Enjoy the designer touches that revel in the elegance of the stone lining the stairway leading to the second level, where you’ll discover four sizable bedrooms and the multipurpose loft. Step into the master retreat—a haven boasting a lavish remodeled bathroom featuring double sinks and an expansive walk-in closet, providing luxury and comfort. New quiet laminate flooring and fresh exterior paint elevate the ambiance, offering a serene atmosphere throughout.  Beyond the elegance indoors, the property accommodates RV parking, brand new insulated garage door, catering to an adventurous lifestyle. Embrace the perfect blend of sophistication and practicality in a prime location, where the allure of a vibrant community merges seamlessly with the tranquility of the golf course surroundings. Welcome home to an oasis of style, comfort, and convenience.*** ALL NEWER STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES STAY INCLUDING WASHER & DRYER.***
